## 승인된 태그 목록

신규 태그 추가는 총괄 PM 승인 필요.

### 공통
`draft`, `active`, `published`, `archived` (status용, frontmatter로 관리)

### UWO
```
uwo, person, event, theme, raw-material
period/joseon, period/dutch-golden-age, period/ming, period/qing
topic/shipwreck, topic/naturalization, topic/weapons, topic/diplomacy
topic/renaissance, topic/art
```

### LAKA
```
cosmetics, analysis, career, concept, entity, source
market/japan, market/us, market/uk, market/eu
channel, distribution
benchmark, m-and-a, odm
hr, risk, interview, brand-strategy
```

### 노무
```
labor, investigation, disciplinary, contract, reference
risk/low, risk/caution, risk/high
```

